title: 611. Top 25 Rookies at Midseason
itunes:title: 611. Top 25 Rookies at Midseason
description:
Daniel Jeremiah and Bucky Brooks are back with a special new episode. To start off, the guys look at the up and coming coaching candidates from Tom Pelissero's recent article (2:37). Then, DJ goes through his top 25 rookies at midseason and Bucky reacts with analysis (11:40).
